com.im.njams.sdk.communication

Interface ShareableReceiver<M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - The raw message type that is received from the transport API
    All Superinterfaces:
    ClasspathValidator, Receiver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SharedHttpSseReceiver, SharedHttpsSseReceiver, SharedJmsReceiver, SharedKafkaReceiver

    public interface ShareableReceiver<M>
extends Receiver
    Interface to be implemented by Receivers that support receiving messages for multiple Njams instances.
    Author:
    cwinkler
